<item>
            <title>[LU-16790] Fix nodemap-related manpages</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16790</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Some issues need to be fixed in man pages related to nodemap, among them:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;lctl-nodemap-modify: section about the &lt;tt&gt;rbac&lt;/tt&gt; property is malformed, regarding line feeds in particular.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;lctl-nodemap-modify: the &lt;tt&gt;forbid_encryption&lt;/tt&gt; property is not mentioned.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;lctl-nodemap-modify: default values for &lt;tt&gt;admin&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;trusted&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;deny_unknown&lt;/tt&gt;, &lt;tt&gt;audit_mode&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;readonly_mount&lt;/tt&gt; properties are not expressed correctly. These properties groks 0 or 1.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
